<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Grovix Lab Portal - Home</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset and basic styling */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Header styling */
        .header {
            background-color: #0078e8; /* Grovix Lab's blue */
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        /* Navbar styling */
        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #005bb5;
        }

        .navbar a {
            color: #fff;
            padding: 14px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .navbar a:hover {
            background-color: #0078e8;
        }

        /* Content styling */
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #005bb5;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }

        /* Footer styling */
        .footer {
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #0078e8;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Grovix Lab Official Portal</h1>
        <p>Welcome to the all-in-one platform for HR, Project Management, Invoicing, and Payment Processing</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <div class="navbar">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/hr">HR</a>
        <a href="/customers">Customers</a>
        <a href="/projects">Projects</a>
        <a href="/invoicing">Invoicing</a>
        <a href="/payments">Payments</a>
        <a href="/support">Support</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Welcome to Grovix Lab Portal</h2>
        <p>
            This portal is your centralized platform for managing all essential functions within Grovix Lab. 
            From handling HR responsibilities and tracking projects to managing invoices and processing payments, 
            we've streamlined every feature to support your workflow efficiently.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Grovix Lab | <a href="#privacy">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="#terms">Terms of Service</a></p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
